<p>John and Dave are back from Macworld with&nbsp;<em>lots</em>&nbsp;of things to report on for you. And, of course, they have your questions to answer, as those piled up while they were away, too. Your two favorite geeks are busy this week, and you&#39;ve got a front row seat. Download, press play, and enjoy!</p>
